I agree there is probably a mundane explanation for the face in this article, however, there 
is no chance of that with my technique, as I&#39;m taking video directly into a pot of water.  
Others have been successful in replicating my simple set-up and have also gotten curious 
results.  One of my images was even confirmed by a forensic lab as being that of my GG-
grandfather.  Here is a link to my 3-min YouTube video:

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dmlox_8H5lo

It&#39;s so easy.  I wish more people would try it!  :-)

Margaret

